title: Amazing homes are waiting for you!
posting_body: ['The Fenley Apartments', '8051 33rd Ave S, Bloomington, MN, 55425', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 43', 'OR Text', '43', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team directly.', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'NOW OPEN!', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 564 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Twin Cities’ newest and most-sophisticated apartment residence is where you’ll find Alcoves, 1, 2, and 3 bedroom apartments offering superior amenities, abundant outdoor space, and elevated design.', 'Taking its name inspiration from the nearby Minnesota Wildlife Refuge trail with its lush, natural landscape, The Fenley beckons you for every adventure, near or far.', 'With the adjacent lightrail, it’s a quick, traffic-free ride to downtown Minneapolis and under 5 minutes from MSP Airport.', 'Bon voyage!', 'The Fenley—it’s modern, it’s convenient, it’s relaxingly chic…offering you the best of the Twin Cities.', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets welcome!', 'Up to 2 pets, dogs and cats welcome.', 'On-site pet run and pet spa!', 'No weight limit!', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Office Hours:', 'Mon-Fri: 9am to 6pm', 'Saturday: 10am to 5pm', 'Sunday: 12pm to 5pm', 'awBtUDG5qO']
